snippet.description:
#PotfsHollywood:Serious as accusation surface in the Johnny Depp Amber heard trial

Johnny Depp allegedly attacked Amber Heard when she withheld his meds while he was supposed to be detoxing on his private Caribbean island, his libel trial heard Thursday.
